---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Base
  title="Body by Olga — Strength & Fitness for Women 40+"
  description="Build real, lasting strength — a fitness platform built for women over 40 who are done with workouts that don't work."
>
  <Nav activePage="home" />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="hero-g">
        <div>
          <p class="hero-ey r">For Women 40+</p>
          <h1 class="r d1">Strong, Energized &amp;<em>Unrecognizable.</em></h1>
          <p class="hero-sub r d2">
            Build real, lasting strength with a method designed specifically for women in midlife — no guesswork, no punishment, just results that actually stick.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-a r d3">
            <a href="/coaching" class="btn btn-p">Apply for Coaching <span class="arr">→</span></a>
            <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-s">Read the Blog</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="r d2">
          <div class="hero-img">
            <img src="/images/hero-image.png" alt="Olga — strength coach for women 40+" loading="eager" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROOF -->
  <div class="proof">
    <div class="ctn">
      <p class="proof-l r">Women just like you have achieved</p>
      <div class="proof-r r d1">
        <span>More Energy</span>
        <span>Real Strength</span>
        <span>Body Confidence</span>
        <span>Lasting Results</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RECOGNITION FLIP CARDS -->
  <section class="recog sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="recog-h r">
        <h2>You weren't supposed to feel like this at 40.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="recog-g">
        <div class="recog-flip flip-card r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front recog-front">
              <p>You're doing <strong>"all the right things"</strong> — eating clean, running regularly — but the weight won't budge. You feel like your body has become a stranger.</p>
              <p class="em">"I'm working harder than ever and getting nowhere."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-recog-1.png" alt="What you've tried" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>This is why what worked before stopped working.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="recog-flip flip-card r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front recog-front">
              <p>You've tried every program, every diet. <strong>Nothing sticks</strong> because none of it was built for your body, your hormones, your life.</p>
              <p class="em">"I feel like I'm starting from zero — again."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-recog-2.png" alt="The struggle" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>You're not failing. The programs are failing you.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="recog-flip flip-card r d3">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front recog-front">
              <p>The energy dips, the sleep issues, the feeling that <strong>your best years are behind you.</strong> You know that's not true. You just need the right tools.</p>
              <p class="em">"I want to feel strong again. Like myself."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-recog-3.png" alt="What's possible" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>You're exactly where you need to be.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
  <section class="philo sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="philo-in">
        <h2 class="r">Your body isn't <em>broken</em>.<br/>It's been given the wrong tools.</h2>
        <div class="philo-cols">
          <div class="philo-col r d1">
            <h3>The Problem</h3>
            <p>Most fitness programs are built for 25-year-old men. They ignore hormonal shifts, recovery needs, and the reality of life after 40. No wonder they don't work.</p>
            <p>Chronic cardio and caloric restriction make things worse — accelerating muscle loss and keeping cortisol elevated.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="philo-col r d2">
            <h3>The Solution</h3>
            <p>Strength training, built around your body's biology. Short, focused sessions that create metabolic change — not exhaustion.</p>
            <p>Real food awareness. Sustainable habits. A program that works with your life, not against it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- METHOD FLIP CARDS -->
  <section class="sp" style="background:var(--bg)">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="system-h r">
        <h2>The Body by Olga Method</h2>
        <p>Four pillars. One integrated system. Designed for your biology.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="system-g">
        <div class="method-flip flip-card r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">01 — STRENGTH</div>
              <h3>Lift to Transform</h3>
              <p>Progressive resistance training, 30 minutes a day. Builds muscle, boosts metabolism, and creates the foundation everything else depends on.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-1.png" alt="Strength training" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Built for how women over 40 actually get strong.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="method-flip flip-card r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">02 — NUTRITION</div>
              <h3>Eat to Fuel</h3>
              <p>No macros to obsess over. No foods to fear. Learn to eat in a way that supports muscle growth, stable energy, and a metabolism that works for you.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-2.png" alt="Nutrition" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Food awareness over food restriction.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="method-flip flip-card r d3">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">03 — RECOVERY</div>
              <h3>Rest to Rebuild</h3>
              <p>Sleep, stress management, and active recovery aren't optional. They're where the actual transformation happens. We build them into the program.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-3.png" alt="Recovery" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>Results are built in the rest, not just the work.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="method-flip flip-card r d4">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front method-front">
              <div class="sys-n">04 — MINDSET</div>
              <h3>Think to Sustain</h3>
              <p>Consistency is a skill. We coach you to build habits that fit your real life — so the results you create are ones you actually keep.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back">
              <img src="/images/flip-method-4.png" alt="Mindset" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="flip-back-overlay"><span>The mental side is where lasting change is made.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APP FLIP CARDS -->
  <section class="app-s sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="app-h r">
        <h2>Everything in one place.</h2>
        <p>Your workouts, nutrition guides, coaching check-ins, and community — all in the Body by Olga app.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="app-g">
        <div class="app-flip flip-card r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i o">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Daily Workouts</h4>
              <p>30-minute sessions, every day. Video demos, timer, and progress tracking built in.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-1.png" alt="Workout screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="app-flip flip-card r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i t">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M11 9H9V2H7v7H5V2H3v7c0 2.12 1.66 3.84 3.75 3.97V22h2.5v-9.03C11.34 12.84 13 11.12 13 9V2h-2v7zm5-3v8h2.5v8H21V2c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 4z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Nutrition Guidance</h4>
              <p>Simple frameworks, meal ideas, and habit tracking — no calorie counting required.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-2.png" alt="Nutrition screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="app-flip flip-card r d3">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i o">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v18l4-4h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>1:1 Coaching</h4>
              <p>Weekly check-ins, form feedback, and personalized program adjustments with Olga.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-3.png" alt="Coaching screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="app-flip flip-card r d1">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i t">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Community</h4>
              <p>A supportive group of women on the same journey. Questions, wins, and accountability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-4.png" alt="Community screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="app-flip flip-card r d2">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i o">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3h-4.18C14.4 1.84 13.3 1 12 1c-1.3 0-2.4.84-2.82 2H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-7 0c.55 0 1 .45 1 1s-.45 1-1 1-1-.45-1-1 .45-1 1-1zm2 14H7v-2h7v2zm3-4H7v-2h10v2zm0-4H7V7h10v2z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Progress Tracking</h4>
              <p>Log your lifts, body measurements, energy levels, and milestones over time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-5.png" alt="Progress tracking screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
        <div class="app-flip flip-card r d3">
          <div class="flip-inner">
            <div class="flip-front app-front">
              <div class="app-i t">
                <svg width="18" height="18" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h4>Education Library</h4>
              <p>Dozens of video lessons on training technique, sleep, stress, and menopause health.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flip-back app-back">
              <img src="/images/app-6.png" alt="Education library screen" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="flip-hint">hover to flip</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MEET OLGA -->
  <section class="meet sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="meet-g">
        <div class="meet-v r">
          <div class="play">
            <svg width="24" height="24" fill="#fff" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="r d2">
          <h2>Meet Olga.</h2>
          <p>I've spent the last 15 years working with women who'd been let down by mainstream fitness. Women who were told to eat less and move more — and were getting worse, not better.</p>
          <p>After my own experience with the hormonal shifts of my 40s, I rebuilt my practice around the science of what actually works for women in midlife. The result is the Body by Olga Method.</p>
          <p class="creds">Certified Strength & Conditioning Specialist (CSCS) · Precision Nutrition Coach · Menopause Fitness Specialist</p>
          <a href="/coaching" class="btn btn-p">Work with me <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section class="testi sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="testi-h r">
        <h2>Real women. Real results.</h2>
        <p>These aren't before/after photos. These are life transformations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-g">
        <div class="testi-c r d1">
          <p class="testi-q">"I've lost 18 lbs and gained more strength than I've had in my 30s."</p>
          <p class="testi-s">I started with Olga at 47, coming off years of cardio that wasn't working. In six months I've completely changed my body composition — and my relationship with exercise.</p>
          <span class="testi-a">Sarah M., 47</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testi-c r d2">
          <p class="testi-q">"The program fits into my life. I actually do it."</p>
          <p class="testi-s">I'm a busy executive with two kids. Every other program I tried required hours I didn't have. 30 minutes a day with Olga's method and I'm the strongest I've ever been.</p>
          <span class="testi-a">Jennifer K., 52</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testi-c r d3">
          <p class="testi-q">"I finally understand how my body works."</p>
          <p class="testi-s">Olga doesn't just give you a workout. She teaches you the why behind everything. I've stopped fighting my body and started working with it. Everything has changed.</p>
          <span class="testi-a">Maria L., 45</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING -->
  <section class="sp" id="pricing">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="price-h r">
        <h2>Simple, transparent pricing.</h2>
        <p>Two ways to work with Olga — both built for real results.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="price-g">
        <div class="pc std r d1">
          <div class="pl">Self-Guided</div>
          <div class="pa">$47</div>
          <div class="pp">/ month</div>
          <div class="pbo">30-day free trial</div>
          <ul class="pf">
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Full workout library</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Nutrition framework</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Community access</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Education library</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="pbtn" onclick="window.location='#pricing'">Start Free Trial</button>
        </div>
        <div class="pc feat r d2">
          <div class="pb">Most Popular</div>
          <div class="pl">1:1 Coaching</div>
          <div class="pa">$297</div>
          <div class="pp">/ month</div>
          <div class="pbo">Application required</div>
          <ul class="pf">
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Everything in Self-Guided</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Weekly 1:1 check-ins</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Custom program adjustments</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Direct messaging</li>
            <li><span class="pk"><svg width="10" height="10" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg></span>Form video reviews</li>
          </ul>
          <button class="pbtn" onclick="window.location='/coaching'">Apply for Coaching</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="fcta sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <h2 class="r">Your strongest decade starts now.</h2>
      <p class="r d1">You've waited long enough. Let's build something real.</p>
      <div class="fcta-a r d2">
        <a href="/coaching" class="btn btn-p">Apply for Coaching <span class="arr">→</span></a>
        <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-g">Read the Blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
